auxiliaryFields: PassFields.AuxiliaryFields: An object that represents the fields that display additional information on the front of a pass. Inherits from PassFields.
backFields: PassFields.BackFields: An object that represents the fields that display information on the back of a pass. Inherits from PassFields.
headerFields: PassFields.HeaderFields: An object that represents the fields that display information at the top of a pass. Inherits from PassFields.
primaryFields: PassFields.PrimaryFields: An object that represents the fields that display the most important information on a pass. Inherits from PassFields.
secondaryFields: PassFields.SecondaryFields: An object that represents the fields that display supporting information on the front of a pass. Inherits from PassFields.
